data.description:
CASH COW!!!!!   New Orleans Style and Charm without the hustle and bustle. This owner is currently collecting $1200 per month on the detached efficiency apartment. The main structure is 3 Bedroom 2 Bath Split Level home tucked away in a secluded area, but minutes from Beautiful City Park, The Lakefront, World Famous Restaurants, and Incredible Night Life. So much to do nearby.
The home has updated counters and cabinets along with beautiful wood floors. The Upper Level has a Full Bath / 2 Bedrooms with one being a huge Primary.  Mid-level has Kitchen / Dining / Living / Laundry set in an open floor plan. Lower level has a Den / Full Bath / 1 Bedroom. BEST OF ALL this home has an INCOME PRODUCING detached 1 Bedroom Guesthouse equipped with a full kitchen, washer & dryer and back-alley entrance & parking. Easy access to I-10, I-610, Canal Street and Metairie Road. 
FLOOD ZONE X.
Don't miss an opportunity to live in one of the most unique cities in the world.
